        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Cancel the Coin Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of the Treasury from minting or issuing any coin, including platinum bullion coins and proof platinum coins, having a nominal or face value exceeding $200.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
